OL,3,CFans 'very disappointed' by WRU
OL,4,Cannouncement on funding of regions
OL,6,FCardiff were taken over by the WRU in
OL,7,FApril after having served formal
OL,8,Fnotification that they intended to
OL,9,Fenter administration. Last week
OL,10,FOspreys and Scarlets said they had
OL,11,Fasked the WRU for assurances that the
OL,12,Ftakeover "will not disproportionally
OL,13,Fbenefit Cardiff and disadvantage the
OL,14,Findependent clubs".
OL,16,FUntil the clubs received more
OL,17,F"clarity" on this, it said both were
OL,18,F"unable to sign the PRA25".
