OL,3,CFans 'very disappointed' by WRU
OL,4,Cannouncement on funding of regions
OL,6,FThis latest announcement from the WRU
OL,7,Fhas left Ospreys and Scarlets fans
OL,8,Fworried about the future of their club.
OL,10,FGareth Storey, from the Scarlets
OL,11,FSupporters Trust, said it was really
OL,12,Fdisappointing to find out the news.
OL,14,FHe said: "We as supporters we met with
OL,15,Fthe WRU several weeks ago and we were
OL,16,Fgiven assurances that the model would
OL,17,Fbe equitable funding and that's
OL,18,Fobviously changed recently.
