OL,4,Cannouncement on funding of regions
OL,6,F"And again - more uncertainty in Welsh
OL,7,Frugby, which is causing complete
OL,8,Fdestabilisation at the end of the
OL,9,Fseason and we want to be able to push
OL,10,Fon and compete for silverware in the
OL,11,Fcoming years to come."
OL,13,FMr Storey feels the WRU is not working
OL,14,Ftogether with the regions.
OL,16,F"I think the WRU needs to take the
OL,17,Fcollaborative approach," he said.
