OL,6,F"By the media leaks and yesterday's
OL,7,Fstatement, it feels like that's not
OL,8,Fthe approach they're looking to take
OL,9,Fat the moment which is very
OL,10,Fdisappointing.
OL,12,F"They need to work with the clubs,
OL,13,FScarlets and Ospreys in particular,
OL,14,Fand they need to give the assurances
OL,15,Fthat have been sought around funding
OL,16,Fand what the future looks like.
