OL,6,F"We've spoken recently, since Abi
OL,7,FTierney came into post 18 months ago,
OL,8,Fabout that collaborative relationship
OL,9,Fand how things between the
OL,10,Fprofessional clubs and the WRU needed
OL,11,Fto improve.
OL,13,F"And then we are still in the same
OL,14,Fsituation it feels like in a week to
OL,15,Fweek, month to month basis - where the
OL,16,Fclubs are almost at war with the WRU
OL,17,Fagain because there isn't agreement."
