OL,3,CFans 'very disappointed' by WRU
OL,4,Cannouncement on funding of regions
OL,6,FFollowing Sunday's announcement, WRU
OL,7,Fchief executive Abi Tierney said: "We
OL,8,Fare continuing to talk to all four
OL,9,Fclubs about what the future will hold.
OL,11,F"We recognise this will be time of
OL,12,Funcertainty and are committed to
OL,13,Ftreating all the clubs, players, and
OL,14,Fsupporters with respect and fairness
OL,15,Fthroughout this process.
OL,17,F"We acknowledge the continued
OL,18,Fcommitment of each club to Welsh rugby
OL,19,Fand will formulate a new plan with the
OL,20,Fbest interests of the whole game in
OL,21,FWales at the forefront of our thinking.
