OL,6,F"When I announced the headline
OL,7,Fstrategy back in July 2024, I said one
OL,8,Fthing is for certain, given the
OL,9,Fchallenges facing rugby in Wales and
OL,10,Fglobally, there will be times when we
OL,11,Fneed to adjust our course. We must
OL,12,Fseize this opportunity."
OL,14,FProfessional Rugby Board chair Malcolm
OL,15,FWall said: "The next phase of
OL,16,Fconsultation, as always, will be
OL,17,Fconducted with the best interests of
OL,18,Fthe whole of Welsh rugby at its heart."
